"linker i ny fane istedenfor i nytt vindu</guilabel>-boksen er krysset av på "
"<guimenuitem>Generelt</guimenuitem>-siden av "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Innstillinger</guimenu><guimenuitem>Oppsett av "
"konqueror</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. &konqueror; kan åpne lenker på sider "
"og <menuchoice><guimenu> Bokmerker</guimenu></menuchoice>, og "
"<guibutton>Hjem</guibutton>, <guibutton>Opp</guibutton>, <guibutton>Tilbake</"
"guibutton> og <guibutton>Framover</guibutton>-elementene i en ny fane eller "
"et nytt vindu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Holding the &Shift; key down while pressing the &MMB; will open the link in "
"the background."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du holder &Shift;-tasten nede samtidig som du trykker &MMB;, vil linken "
"åpnes i bakgrunnen."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> Mouse Button Menus"
msgstr "<mousebutton>Høyre</mousebutton> museknapp-menyer"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:278
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Clicking the &RMB; on almost any part of &konqueror;'s window will bring "
#| "up an appropriate context menu."
msgid ""
"Clicking the &RMB; on almost any part of &konqueror;’s window will bring up "
"an appropriate context menu."
msgstr ""
"Du kan klikke &RMB; nesten hvor som helst i &konqueror;-vinduet og du vil få "
"fram en passende meny."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:281
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you have enabled the <guilabel>Right click goes back in history</"
#| "guilabel> option in &konqueror;'s <link linkend=\"othersettings\"> "
#| "configuration</link> settings a simple <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> "
#| "click is equivalent to clicking on the <guibutton>Back</guibutton> "
#| "button. In this case you can access the context menu by moving the mouse "
#| "with the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> button held down."
msgid ""
"If you have enabled the <guilabel>Right click goes back in history</"
"guilabel> option in &konqueror;’s <link linkend=\"othersettings\"> "
"configuration</link> settings a simple <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> "
"click is equivalent to clicking on the <guibutton>Back</guibutton> button. "
"In this case you can access the context menu by moving the mouse with the "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> button held down."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du har skrudd på valget <guilabel>Høyreklikk går bakover i historien</"
"guilabel> i &konqueror; sitt <link linkend=\"othersettings\"> oppsett</"
