"til elementet og lar deg endre rettighetene."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy and Rename"
msgstr "Kopiering og navneendring"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1127
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you want to make a copy of an existing file with a different name -- "
